---
// src/pages/reviews/iphone-16-pro-review.astro
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="iPhone 16 Pro Review 2026 - Is It Worth Upgrading?">
  <article class="review">
    <header class="review-header">
      <span class="category">Apple</span>
      <h1>iPhone 16 Pro Review: Is It Worth Upgrading in 2026?</h1>
      <div class="meta">
        <span>By Tech Reviewer</span>
        <span>•</span>
        <span>March 5, 2026</span>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="rating">
      <span class="score">4.5</span>
      <span class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
    </div>

    <div class="toc">
      <h2>Table of Contents</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#overview">Overview</a></li>
        <li><a href="#design">Design & Display</a></li>
        <li><a href="#camera">Camera</a></li>
        <li><a href="#performance">Performance</a></li>
        <li><a href="#battery">Battery Life</a></li>
        <li><a href="#verdict">Verdict</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The iPhone 16 Pro represents Apple's latest flagship smartphone, featuring the new A18 Pro chip, improved camera system, and a refined design. But is it worth upgrading from your current iPhone?</p>
      
      <div class="pros-cons">
        <div class="pros">
          <h3>Pros</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>✅ Excellent camera quality</li>
            <li>✅ A18 Pro chip is incredibly fast</li>
            <li>✅ Beautiful ProMotion display</li>
            <li>✅ Improved battery life</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="cons">
          <h3>Cons</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>❌ Expensive starting price</li>
            <li>❌ No major design changes</li>
            <li>❌ Charging speed could be faster</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="design">
      <h2>Design & Display</h2>
      <p>The iPhone 16 Pro features a 6.3-inch Super Retina XDR display with ProMotion technology. The display is stunning, with vibrant colors and deep blacks that make everything from photos to videos look incredible.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="camera">
      <h2>Camera</h2>
      <p>Apple has made significant improvements to the camera system. The new 48MP main sensor captures more detail than ever, and the improved Night mode makes low-light photography a breeze.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="performance">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <p>The A18 Pro chip delivers blazing-fast performance. Whether you're gaming, editing videos, or just browsing the web, the iPhone 16 Pro handles everything with ease.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="battery">
      <h2>Battery Life</h2>
      <p>Battery life has improved significantly. Most users will easily get through a full day of heavy use, with some getting up to two days on a single charge with moderate usage.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="verdict">
      <h2>Verdict</h2>
      <p>The iPhone 16 Pro is an excellent smartphone that delivers in all the key areas. If you're coming from an iPhone 14 Pro or earlier, it's definitely worth upgrading. iPhone 15 Pro users can skip this generation unless camera is your top priority.</p>
      
      <div class="buy-links">
        <h3>Where to Buy</h3>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0D1XD1ZV3?tag=rc0440-20" class="buy-btn" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
          Buy on Amazon
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .review {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .review-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .category {
    background: #667eea;
    color: white;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .review-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .meta {
    color: #666;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .rating {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .score {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #667eea;
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-left: 1rem;
  }

  .toc {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .toc h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .toc ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .toc li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .toc a {
    color: #667eea;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #333;
  }

  section p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pros-cons {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pros, .cons {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .pros {
    background: #e8f5e9;
  }

  .cons {
    background: #ffebee;
  }

  .pros h3, .cons h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .pros ul, .cons ul {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .pros li, .cons li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .buy-links {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .buy-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 3rem;
    background: #ff9900;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .buy-btn:hover {
    background: #e68a00;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .pros-cons {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .review-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
